      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（寮の玄関には、人だかりが出来ていた）\n（その正体は、マスコミの記者達だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(There’s a crowd at the front door to the dorm.)\n(It’s made up of reporters.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8891873571607807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.45319709777832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "勝手に入らないで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ don’t come in!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.45319709777832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 10.113151645660396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "だから、さくらちゃんはいないって言ってるんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the last time‚ Sakura isn’t home!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.113151645660398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 13.341405725479156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（遙子さんと沙季が追い返そうと必死に対応していた）\n（二人を守るため、俺は間に割って入った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Haruko and Saki are desperately trying to drive them away.)\n(I step in to protect the girls.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.08411170641582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんですか？　ここは私有地です\n出ていって下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you want? This is private property.\nPlease leave.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.25224995613099,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 20.57827649116517
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あなた、マネージャーさんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re the manager‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.754932351734332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今回のこと、ご存じだったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you know anything about this scandal?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.03621070765069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob2",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "事務所の三枝社長は最初から知ってて採用した",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our sources say that President Saegusa of your agency",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.66314100804537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob2",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "という話も出ていますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "knew all about it from the very start!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.001649486845814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "知る訳ないでしょう？\n根も葉もない噂です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How could he have known?\nIt’s just groundless gossip.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.22980767471203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "川咲さくらさんが心臓移植を受けたのは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Sakura Kawasaki did have a heart transplant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.600828023578806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 39.600828023578856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "事実ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t that correct?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.100828023578806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 44.763843675281734
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 48.99001072582443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "その通りですがドナーについては患者に知らされません\n私も事務所も、本人も分かりません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She did. But transplant patients aren’t told anything about their donors.\nNeither myself nor the agency nor Sakura herself know anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.99001072582443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob2",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ということは、心臓が長瀬麻奈さんのものだという",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you’re saying that her heart could belong to Mana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.506677201756226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob2",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "可能性もある、ということですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t that correct?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.00667720175623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今は、彼女達の未来がかかったグランプリの最中です\n取材を受ける時間はありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The girls are right in the middle of the Grand Prix—their future is on the line.\nThey don’t have time for an interview.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.89001053508957,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7400.00000000002,
          "startTime": 66.45667720175625
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7400.00000000002,
          "startTime": 66.45667720175625
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_corridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 66.25667720175623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すまない。二人に対応させてしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry you two had to handle that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.92334386842289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7242963506464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで。私は芸能人になって初めて\nあれだけの記者に囲まれてちょっと嬉しかったかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about it. That’s the first time since becoming an idol\nthat I’ve had that many reporters around me. I kinda liked it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.90243690348505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます、遙子さん\nさくらと琴乃は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Haruko.\nWhere are Sakura and Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.45935326751905,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2199.9999999999745,
          "startTime": 88.65935326751902
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "リビングにいるよ\nこっちこっち",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the living room.\nThis way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.05935326751904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 93.42601993418572
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 93.65935326751904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}… The lesson is",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.42601993418576,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7.313399147577115,
          "startTime": 94.43333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "さくら。気にしなくていい\n今はグランプリに集中しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ don’t worry about it.\nFocus on the Grand Prix for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.81012427346752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "……はい\nでも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Me too.\nBut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.67679094013413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "教えられないってどういうことです？\n私は長瀬麻奈の妹だと言ってるじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean you can’t tell me?\nFor the tenth time‚ I’m Mana Nagase’s younger sister!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 104.76666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "教えられないって……実の妹ですよ！　姉の臓器が誰に\n移植されたか知る権利が……え……そうなんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why can’t you tell me? I’m her sister! I have a right to know\nwho received her donated organ! Huh? Oh… I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.60577057537287,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12166.666666666686,
          "startTime": 123.30577057537276
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "たとえ親族でも、相手のプライバシーに関わることは\n教えられないって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said they’re not allowed to disclose the private information\nof their patients‚ even to family members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.03910390870615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "外国だと、よくドナーと患者が会ってるなんて話\n聞きますけど……",
